title: ovarian cancer: O1
extract_protocol_ch1: Total cellular RNA was isolated from tumor tissue, using the Qiagen Rneasy Mini Kit.
label_protocol_ch1: cDNA was synthesised from 5 µg total RNA by reverse transcription, synthesis of biotin-labeled cRNA was performed using the BioArray High Yield RNA Transcription kit.
hyb_protocol: The fragmented cRNA was hybridised to HGU133 arrays at 45 °C in a hybridization oven for 16 hr.
scan_protocol: Chip scanning was done with an Affymetrix Gene Array Scanner G2500A.
data_processing: Signals and detection calls were calculated with the R package affy according to the standard MAS 5.0 protocol of the chip manufacturer.
